<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.10.2">
<l>kuṟaivi ṟaṭaṅkaṭal kōḷḷara vēṟittaṉ kōlaccen tāmaraikkaṇ</l>
<l>uṟaipavaṉ pōlavōr yōkupuṇarnta voḷimaṇi vaṇṇaṉ kaṇṇaṉ</l>
<l>kaṟaiyaṇi mūkkuṭaip puḷḷaik kaṭāvi yacuraraik kāyntavammāṉ</l>
<l>niṟaipuka ḻēttiyum pāṭiyu māṭiyum yāṉoru muṭṭilaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who mounted the murderous serpent on the vast ocean without want, like the one who stays</l>
<l>with beatiful red lotus eyes, the one with bright sapphire colour who is joined in unique yoga, Kṛṣṇa,</l>
<l>the lord who rages against the asuras, driving the bird with a spot-adorned nose,</l>
<l>praising his] full fame, singing and dancing I am without any obstacle.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
